Description:
 uc-tool-mx - Generate and inject AMD/Intel microcode CPIO images into initrd
Changes:
 uc-tool-mx (26.06.1) mx; urgency=medium
 .
   * Add bash-completion for uc-tool.
   * Clarify --extract and --list help/man page: show valid modes in
     syntax line, replace ambiguous "(bare)" with "ucode [default]".
   * debian/rules: inject version and date from changelog into installed
     script and man page.
   * --list: show compression name in brackets (e.g. [gzip]) instead of
     file extension ([gz]) for the main initrd section.
